nodes.text: Yiprukk was a young Force-sensitive Wookiee male. During the Clone Wars, Yiprukk was kidnapped by a Trandoshan hunter, forcing a group of individuals associated with the Jedi Order and the Galactic Republic, along with Wookiees, to track down and rescue Yiprukk.
Yiprukk was mentioned in Collapse of the Republic, a roleplaying supplementary sourcebook for the Star Wars Roleplaying series that was published by Fantasy Flight Games in 2019.
